<p>No matter what kind of <script>function ga4_link97() { window.dataLayer.push(JSON.parse('{"event":"click_inarticle"}')) }</script><a href="https://reviewed.usatoday.com/gift-guides/features/gifts-for-mom" onclick="ga4_link97()">mom</a> she is—a beach lover, a homebody, or a glamor gal—there's something on this list that's sure to be a great gift for her.</p>

<p>Here are 23 thoughtful Mother's Day gifts for your wife: </p>

